# Website Creation Guide

This README provides a structured overview of best practices and steps for creating your own website, especially for beginners. Follow this guide to organize your files, write clean code, and build a maintainable, responsive site.

---

## Table of Contents

1. [Project Structure](#1-project-structure)
2. [HTML Best Practices](#2-html-best-practices)
3. [CSS Best Practices](#3-css-best-practices)
4. [JavaScript Best Practices](#4-javascript-best-practices)
5. [Images and Assets](#5-images-and-assets)
6. [Version Control](#6-version-control)
7. [Documentation](#7-documentation)
8. [Going Live](#8-going-live)
9. [Accessibility & SEO](#9-accessibility--seo)
10. [Example: Minimal HTML File](#10-example-minimal-html-file)

